title: [Surname Registry]
description: Airy and open, this white-walled room is awash in sunlight.  A vase of ladyslipper orchids sits nearly alone on a long bleached pine table surrounded by high-backed chairs.  In the center of the dark walnut floor is a tasseled silk rug in shades of sage and amber.

Airy and open, this white-walled room glimmers in the moonlight.  A vase of ladyslipper orchids sits nearly alone on a long bleached pine table surrounded by high-backed chairs.  In the center of the dark walnut floor is a tasseled silk rug in shades of sage and amber.
